title: [Veythorne Manor, Lake]
description: The long reeds rustle and whisper with every passing breeze, and the ripples upon the water echo with the same soft resonance.  Sunlight glints like faceted jewels upon the surface of the water, and a small ivory-hued dock is directly to the southwest.
